JIT-compile Exo language procedures to MLIR or native code.

usage:

    $ uv run xdsl-exo examples/demo.py  # mlir
    $ uv run python examples/demo.py    # native

how it works:

      Exo Python source
          v
      Exo LoopIR
          v
    - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - xDSL
      MLIR module
          v
      MLIR LLVM dialect
          v
    - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - llvmlite
      Native code

references:

- https://xdsl.dev/
- https://github.com/xdslproject/xdsl
- https://exo-lang.dev/
- https://github.com/exo-lang/exo/blob/main/docs/README.md
- https://github.com/kaylendog/exo-mlir
